                <h2>Agreement</h2>
                <p>These terms apply when you use MapleKiosk websites, software, apps, or services. By using MapleKiosk, you agree to follow them.</p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2>Accounts</h2>
                <p>You are responsible for your account information, password security, and activity under your account. Tell us quickly if you suspect unauthorized access.</p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2>Acceptable Use</h2>
                <p>Use MapleKiosk for lawful business purposes only. Do not misuse the service, disrupt it, attempt unauthorized access, or use it for illegal or harmful activity.</p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2>Customer Data</h2>
                <p>You own the business data you put into MapleKiosk. You allow us to host, process, back up, and display that data so we can provide the service.</p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2>Billing</h2>
                <p>Plan prices, billing cycles, trials, taxes, cancellations, and refunds are based on the plan or agreement you choose. Fees are non-refundable unless stated otherwise or required by law.</p>
